      "text": [
        " اَلنَّبِيُّ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ : \"مَنْ شَهِدَ عِنْدَنَا بِشَهَادَةٍ ثُمَّ غَيَّرَ أَخَذْنَا بِالْأُولَى وَ طَرَحْنَا اَلْأُخْرَى\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3289 - And the Prophet, may Allah (swt) bless him and his family, said:\n\"Whoever testifies before us with a testimony and then changes it, we will accept the first (testimony) and discard the second (testimony).\""
        ]
      }
    },
